Voyager 1 48-sec averaged magnetic field data tab-delimited ascii files. 

The columns are:
1. SC   ID (Voyager 1)
2  year (2013)
3. DOY (Jan 1 = 1)
4. F1 (the magnetic field strength, the average of higher resolution field strengths, in nT)
5, 6, 7 BR, BT, BN (the magnetic field components in RTN coordinates, in nT)

The one sigma uncertainty is dBR ~= 0.02 nT and dBT ~= 0.02 nT. The uncertainty in dBN is larger, since we could not obtain this from a magrol; it could be between 0.02 nT and 0.1 nT. 

